This works for me with the latest from the testing branch:

{code}
# euca_conf --deregister-osg OSG_16
SERVICE	objectstorage     	objectstorage	OSG_16               	arn:euca:bootstrap:objectstorage:objectstorage:OSG_16/
{code}

Note that you should be passing the name of a registered OSG to the command.
